title: Japanese Art Collection 2023 Wall Calendar
description:
A home and office necessity to keep track of important dates, this Japanese Art Collection wall calendar in 12"x12" format is made with only the highest quality paper and printing methods featuring stunning, carefully-curated imagery. Calendar features a 4-month preview page of the following year, before & after preview months on each page, and includes public & culturally significant holidays.
  • Dimensions: 12"x 12"
  • Materials: Pink holographic foil details
  • 3 languages: English, French, & Spanish
